	Item 2.02






	Results of Operations and Financial Condition.












	On April 5, 2017, Remark Media, Inc. (“we”, “us” or “our”) issued a press release announcing our financial results for the fourth quarter and year ended December 31, 2016, updating portions of a release we issued on March 30, 2017. Copies of the releases are furnished herewith as Exhibit 99.1 and Exhibit 99.2, respectively.









